# Client onboarding checklist

Client: {{ client_name }}
Site: {{ url }}
Plan: {{ plan_name }}
Price: {{ currency }} {{ price_monthly }}/month

## Before first weekly run

- Confirm client email
- Confirm target website URL
- Confirm report format
- Confirm brand name
- Confirm report delivery cadence
- Run first report manually
- Review report before sending
- Add client to weekly job

## First report command

```bash
python -m app.main --url {{ url }} --brand-name "{{ brand_name }}" --client-name "{{ client_name }}" --format {{ format }}
```

## Weekly batch command

```bash
python -m app.weekly --job-file data/weekly_jobs.example.json --mode outbox
```
